<paragraph id="5E2E361FFFB8514E5E3FAAA1FB56F91D" blockId="72.[290,1686,960,1828]" pageId="72" pageNumber="145">
Most of the 
<collectingCountry id="2686768FFFB8514E5D16AAA1FD4FF9B2" box="[589,693,1531,1572]" name="Guam" pageId="72" pageNumber="145">Guam</collectingCountry>
